            <title>[LU-12782] Convert cl_object_attr_lock to rwlock</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12782</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Under some shared file workloads, the cl_object_attr_lock ends up &apos;hot&apos;.&#160; As suggested in an old comment, it can easily be converted to an rwlock, which is useful because it is often taken for read.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
